'''Orion'''

#(''Greek mythology'') A [[giant]]-[[hunter]], [[pursuer]] of the [[Pleiades]] and [[lover]] of [[Eos]], and [[kill]]ed by [[Artemis]].
#A [[constellation]] on the [[celestial]] [[equator]] close to [[Gemini]] and [[Taurus]], containing the [[star]]s [[Betelgeuse]] and [[Rigel]].

====Synonyms====
*(''constellation''): the [[Hunter]]

